Escape sequences should not be used in text blocks
Why is this an issue? The use of escape sequences is mostly unnecessary in text blocks. 
### Noncompliant
String textBlock = """
        \"\"\" this \nis
        text  block!
        !!!!
      """;
### Compliant
String textBlock = """
        \""" this
        is
        text  block!
        !!!!
      """;
### Noncompliant
{{BUGGY}}
### Compliant
